LARDD 1
TITLE RTL8139 Driver File
TEXT Realtek RTL8139 PCI network adapter DRFL 2 code file.
SECTION Files
ITEM drv-rtl8139.drfl -> DRFL 2 code file for PCI 10EC:8139.
ITEM rtl8139.rxr -> install bundle containing drv-rtl8139.drfl and driverctl.rxe.
SECTION Install
ITEM rxr verify A:rtl8139.rxr
ITEM rxr install A:rtl8139.rxr
ITEM drivers reload
ITEM drivers show rtl8139
ITEM drivers
END
